class Solution(object):
    def maxOperations(self, s):
        """
        :type s: str
        :rtype: int
        """
        count = 0
        one_counter = 0
        prev_ele = ""
        for i, ele in enumerate(s):
            if ele == "1":
                one_counter += 1
                prev_ele = "1"
                continue
            if prev_ele == "0":
                continue
            prev_ele = "0"
            # 10
            print(i, one_counter)
            count += one_counter
        return count
